name: Crown Bolt Zinc-Plated Steel Screw Eye Lag Threaded Bolts (25-Pack)
description: These screw eyes are bolts with a formed closed circular eye fashioned at the non-threaded end and lag threaded screws on the other. Great for light-duty applications, the screw eye is made with steel for strength and is designed to attach cables or rope to surfaces. Use with rope or cable which has the same load rating. Use pre-drilled hole.California residents: see Proposition 65 information25 pieces per packSteel constructionZinc-plated#6
